Sentencas: In this paper, the Sr2MnO4 preparation process was optimized via high energy ball milling and calcination.
Titulo: Impact of Sr2MnO4 preparation process on its electrical resistivity

Sentencas: The optimal process conditions were a ball milling time of 3 h, sintering temperature of 1000 degrees C, sintering time of 10 h, and double cycling.
Titulo: Impact of Sr2MnO4 preparation process on its electrical resistivity

Sentencas: The lowest resistivity achieved with the optimized process was 0.142 Omega m.
Titulo: Impact of Sr2MnO4 preparation process on its electrical resistivity

Sentencas: The sintering temperature was decreased after the optimization process with an associated increase in preparation efficiency and reduction in calcination time.
Titulo: Impact of Sr2MnO4 preparation process on its electrical resistivity
